description: This file defines a data model for a movie script, sets up an agent with an OpenAI chat model, and runs the agent to generate a movie script based on an image.

classes.name: MovieScript
classes.description: A Pydantic model representing the structure of a movie script, including name, setting, characters, and storyline.

methods.name: agent.run
methods.description: Executes the agent to generate a movie script based on the provided prompt and images.
